      VALUES ("People never play  Abaddon as a carry,but he is hella good.I mean,immagine this: Curse of Avernus is a slow with an attack speed steroid,you have a heal/nuke,you have the shield to remove the negative buffs from yourself,and he has  Borrowed Time,to make you survivable", "Focus on last hitting.Try to exploit the mistakes of your enemies and net early kills with the help of your support.Remember though,that you cannot use death coil on yourself,and make sure you use  Aphotic Shield smartly.", "At this point you should have already aquired your core.Try to be in fights,as your DPS might be higher than you expect. Curse of Avernus+ Mask of Madness+ Skull Basher will make sure that no enemy escapes from you.<br/>Try to build-up to your luxury items as fast as possible so you don't fall behind.Abuse the power that  Abaddon has early to mid game.", "You probably have at least 2 luxury items in your inventory at this point.If that is so,than good for you.You have done well until now,and you should probably do well in late game.<br/> Beware though,people that are illusion based: Chaos Knight, Naga Siren, Phantom Lancer,might cause you trouble.Remember to tell one of your teammates to get some heavy AoE to counter their presence,or a silence to stop them from replicating(though it doesn't stop  Phantom Lancer do it.)", "Versatility in one word (Carry)", "dotafire", "Wulfstan", "http://www.dotafire.com/dota-2/guide/versatility-in-one-word-abaddon-3935","Abaddon", "57");
